Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.28,0:22:06.36,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}憎恶累累不堪重负
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.36,0:22:11.48,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}虚实如鲜花遍地绽放结实
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.48,0:22:16.91,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}却是梦的瑕疵 遭人唾弃的脏腑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.46,0:22:26.07,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}搭上这双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.37,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}赌上这条命
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.92,0:22:38.04,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}即将面对时 苍白地打开手指
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.06,0:22:44.00,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}如果你是暗杀者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.01,0:22:50.41,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}是否就能粉碎迷惑心 嫉妒心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.70,*OP_cht,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}痛苦昏厥吧
